OL,3,CArrears on household bills surge 25%
OL,4,Camong those in debt ` charity
OL,6,FArrears on household bills have surged
OL,7,Fby 25% among those seeking debt advice
OL,8,Fas April bill hikes loom, a charity
OL,9,Fhas warned.
OL,11,FThe StepChange debt charity said its
OL,12,Faverage client was #3,911 in arrears
OL,13,Fon household bills, up from #3,124 in
OL,14,F2023.
OL,16,FOverall, the average amount of debt
OL,17,Ffor each StepChange client jumped 7%,
OL,18,Ffrom #16,706 in 2023 to #17,936 last
OL,19,Fyear.
