OL,3,CArrears on household bills surge 25%
OL,4,Camong those in debt ` charity
OL,6,FMortgage arrears saw the most dramatic
OL,7,Frise, soaring by 69% from #6,054 in
OL,8,F2023 to #10,239.
OL,10,FAlmost a fifth of StepChange clients
OL,11,F(18%) with a mortgage are now in
OL,12,Farrears, the charity said.
OL,14,FHowever, the proportion of clients
OL,15,Fwith a mortgage remained low at 14%.
OL,17,FEnergy arrears have risen by 28% year
OL,18,Fon year, with a 58% jump since 2022,
OL,19,Ffrom #1,485 to #2,340 last year.
