OL,6,FThe average monthly income among
OL,7,Fclients was also up 7% year on year,
OL,8,Fstanding at #1,874 in 2024.
OL,10,FStepChange chief executive Vikki
OL,11,FBrownridge said: "As we mark the start
OL,12,Fof Debt Awareness Week, it's important
OL,13,Fto shine a light on the reality for
OL,14,Fthose facing debt issues in 2025.
