OL,3,CArrears on household bills surge 25%
OL,4,Camong those in debt ` charity
OL,6,F"We've now seen a consistent trend of
OL,7,Fdebt levels deepening over the last
OL,8,Ffew years, with the most severe rises
OL,9,Foccurring in the household arrears our
OL,10,Fclients have, particularly when it
OL,11,Fcomes to mortgage, council tax and
OL,12,Fenergy debt.
OL,14,F"This is something which could worsen
OL,15,Fas many bills are set to rise further
OL,16,Fnext month.
