OL,3,CArrears on household bills surge 25%
OL,4,Camong those in debt ` charity
OL,6,F"Consistently rising living costs are
OL,7,Fpulling higher earners into debt, with
OL,8,Fmore people finding work is not
OL,9,Fshielding them against financial
OL,10,Fhardship.
OL,12,F"Those on the lowest incomes face
OL,13,Fgrowing budget deficits and it's a
OL,14,Fconcern that this could be pushing
OL,15,Fmore people to rely on credit to make
OL,16,Fends meet.
OL,18,F"At this week's Spring Statement, it's
OL,19,Fimportant the Government does not
OL,20,Fexacerbate hardship for the most
OL,21,Ffinancially vulnerable households.
